class="landing-feed--story-content">
<a
class="landing-feed--story-title link link-txt" href="/news-politics/politics/news/a34120/today-at-the-cafe/">Sam Brownback Drops By For A Bite</a><div
class="landing-feed--story-abstract">
In which we learn that you can never tell about the guy on the next stool at the cafe.
<span
class="byline--author ">
By
<a
href="http://www.esquire.com/author/7884/charles-pierce/" class="link link-txt byline--author-name" rel="author">Charles Pierce</a>		</span></div></div></div><div
